query DashboardContentQuery(
  $first: Int!
  $after: String
) {
  trades(first: $first, after: $after, orderBy: "executionTime_DESC") {
    edges {
      cursor
      node {
        id
        tradeId
        symbol
        side
        quantity
        price
        totalValue
        traderId
        clientId
        accountId
        orderType
        status
        executionTime
        commission
        fees
        currency
        settlementDate
        tradeDate
      }
    }
    pageInfo {
      hasNextPage
      hasPreviousPage
      startCursor
      endCursor
    }
    totalCount
  }
}
